OL,3,CChris Brown pleads guilty to affray
OL,4,Cafter Mayfair nightclub confrontation
OL,6,FR&B singer Chris Brown has pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to affray- the use or threat of
OL,8,Funlawful violence- after a
OL,9,Fconfrontation at a Mayfair club in
OL,10,F2023.
OL,12,FThe singer arrived at Southwark Crown
OL,13,FCourt today, waving to a group of fans
OL,14,Fon his way in.
OL,16,FThe fans held signs, with one
OL,17,Freportedly shouting "I love you Chris"
OL,18,Fas he walked past.
OL,20,FThe hearing took less than five
OL,21,Fminutes.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/3
