OL,3,CChris Brown pleads guilty to affray
OL,4,Cafter Mayfair nightclub confrontation
OL,6,FThe 37 year old had been due to face a
OL,7,Fjury trial on October 26 after
OL,8,Fpleading not guilty, in June last
OL,9,Fyear, to a charge of assault
OL,10,Foccasioning actual bodily harm.
OL,12,FBrown denied having an offensive
OL,13,Fweapon, a bottle, in a public place,
OL,14,Fand denied a charge of attempting to
OL,15,Fcause grievous bodily harm.
OL,17,FThese charges have now been
OL,18,Fdiscontinued and he will be sentenced
OL,19,Fon October 26 for the affray charge.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/3
