OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1784899119
OL,3,CChris Brown pleads guilty to affray
OL,4,Cafter Mayfair nightclub confrontation
OL,6,FHe was charged alongside his vocal
OL,7,Fcoach, Omololu Akinlolu who had also
OL,8,Fdenied assault occasioning actual
OL,9,Fbodily harm and has now pleaded guilty
OL,10,Fto affray.
OL,12,FHe will be sentenced on the same date.
